foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: At the end of FY2015, NARA reported 8,325 pending and backlogged requests, but noted that it was cleaning up the FOIA data in its data warehouse. Previously, the data in the warehouse did not consistently reflect all request closures. This resulted in a higher number of requests reported as pending at the end of FY2015. The change from 8,325 to 4,396 reflects the cleanup to the data warehouse and accurately reflects the number of pending requests at the start of FY2016.
